1
00:00:02,980 --> 00:00:04,500
[Yongkyu: Now that everyone's back...]

2
00:00:04,500 --> 00:00:06,100
[Hyeyeon: The order...]
[Jinwoo: We can start.]

3
00:00:06,100 --> 00:00:08,510
[Sujin: Why don't we start from number 8?]

4
00:00:08,510 --> 00:00:11,180
[Yongkyu: Oh, no way. No way.]

5
00:00:10,810 --> 00:00:12,200
-Start from No. 1. -No, really.

6
00:00:11,180 --> 00:00:13,780
[Hyeyeon: No, really.]

7
00:00:13,990 --> 00:00:14,700
No way.

8
00:00:15,940 --> 00:00:17,900
[Upset]

9
00:00:15,960 --> 00:00:17,050
No, no.

10
00:00:18,700 --> 00:00:20,520
[Sujin: Should I go first?]

11
00:00:27,990 --> 00:00:29,220
[Sujin: I want a single room.]

12
00:00:31,200 --> 00:00:33,870
[Hyeyeon: I don't really want a single.]

13
00:00:35,470 --> 00:00:39,200
[Sujin: Honestly, I wanted
to invite someone over to my room.]

14
00:00:39,200 --> 00:00:42,410
[Sujin: It can be a private space
for just the two of us.]

15
00:00:42,410 --> 00:00:45,610
[Sujin: It's basically an indoor date
if you think about it.]

16
00:00:45,610 --> 00:00:49,880
[Sujin: It was a better way]

17
00:00:49,880 --> 00:00:52,280
[Sujin: to get closer.]

18
00:00:53,890 --> 00:00:54,690
[Eunchae: I'll...]

19
00:00:56,240 --> 00:00:57,500
[Eunchae: I'll choose the triple room.]

20
00:00:57,500 --> 00:00:59,220
[Hyeyeon: Which spot?]
[Yongkyu: Congrats... wait, what?]

21
00:00:59,220 --> 00:01:01,040
[Eunchae: We get to choose that, too?]
[Hyeyeon: Yeah.]

22
00:01:01,040 --> 00:01:03,620
[Jinwoo: Oh, we even have
to choose the specific bed?]
[Yongkyu: Like the single or double one. Ah...]

23
00:01:02,340 --> 00:01:03,700
-Like the single or double one. -Really?

24
00:01:03,620 --> 00:01:06,540
[Eunchae—Triple Room]
[Eunchae: Then I definitely
want the single bed.]

25
00:01:05,129 --> 00:01:06,540
-Single bed. -Single bed.

26
00:01:06,540 --> 00:01:08,860
[Heejin: This is driving me crazy.]

27
00:01:11,240 --> 00:01:13,910
[Eunchae: I don't open up to people easily,]

28
00:01:13,910 --> 00:01:17,300
[Eunchae: so staying with everyone]

29
00:01:17,300 --> 00:01:19,430
[Eunchae: would make me feel more comfortable.]

30
00:01:19,430 --> 00:01:22,900
[Eunchae: It'd also]

31
00:01:22,900 --> 00:01:24,500
[Eunchae: help us bond.]

32
00:01:24,500 --> 00:01:29,039
[Eunchae: I didn't pick the quad room.]

33
00:01:29,039 --> 00:01:31,180
[Eunchae: Cause I wanted my own bed]

34
00:01:31,180 --> 00:01:33,850
[Eunchae: and he triple room happened to have one.]

35
00:01:34,500 --> 00:01:38,060
[Hyeyeon: Since the single bed
in the triple room was taken,]

36
00:01:38,060 --> 00:01:41,320
[Hyeyeon—Quad Room]
[Hyeyeon: I'll just go
with the wall bed in the quad room.]

37
00:01:41,660 --> 00:01:42,900
[Gasps]

38
00:01:43,150 --> 00:01:43,800
-By the wall, by the wall. -What's wrong?

39
00:01:43,190 --> 00:01:45,590
[Hyeyeon: What's wrong?
Why is everyone acting like this?]

40
00:01:43,800 --> 00:01:44,450
Why is everyone reacting like this?

41
00:01:44,450 --> 00:01:45,479
The wall bed.

42
00:01:45,590 --> 00:01:49,300
[Hyeyeon: It was colder over by the triple room,]

43
00:01:49,300 --> 00:01:52,530
[Hyeyeon: so I chose the quad room]

44
00:01:52,530 --> 00:01:55,100
[Hyeyeon: closest to the living room.]

45
00:01:55,100 --> 00:01:57,870
[Eunchae—Triple Room]
[Chaebe: I'll take the triple room...]

46
00:01:57,870 --> 00:02:00,900
[Eunchae—Triple Room]
[Chaebe: The bed in the back.]

47
00:01:59,120 --> 00:02:00,410
The bed in the back.

48
00:02:01,100 --> 00:02:03,220
[Struggling]

49
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:04,500
[Jinwoo: Hyeyeon, you picked No. 1, right?]

50
00:02:04,500 --> 00:02:07,460
[Hyeyeon—Quad Room]
[Jinwoo: Bed 1 in the quad?]
[Hyeyeon: I think so.]

51
00:02:07,730 --> 00:02:09,860
[Jinwoo: My mind was racing because]

52
00:02:09,860 --> 00:02:12,800
[Jinwoo: I really wanted to room with Seungho.]

53
00:02:12,800 --> 00:02:16,270
[Jinwoo: And it happened
to be one bed with 2 pillows.]

54
00:02:16,270 --> 00:02:17,600
[Jinwoo: That felt pretty exciting. So]

55
00:02:17,600 --> 00:02:19,740
[Jinwoo: I was the 5th to choose,]

56
00:02:19,740 --> 00:02:22,140
[Jinwoo: and Seungho was 6th. So]

57
00:02:22,140 --> 00:02:23,740
[Jinwoo: I was like,]

58
00:02:23,740 --> 00:02:25,610
[Jinwoo: "If you feel the same way right now,"]

59
00:02:25,610 --> 00:02:28,540
[Jinwoo: "you'll definitely
pick the spot next to me."]

60
00:02:28,540 --> 00:02:29,340
[Hyeyeon & Jinwoo—Quad Room]

61
00:02:29,340 --> 00:02:31,620
[Hyeyeon & Jinwoo—Quad Room]
[Jinwoo: Then I'll take bed 4 in the quad room.]

62
00:02:31,220 --> 00:02:32,650
-Okay. -The one on the very edge.

63
00:02:31,620 --> 00:02:33,100
[Hyeyeon & Jinwoo—Quad Room]
[Jinwoo: The one on the edge.]

64
00:02:33,350 --> 00:02:35,780
[Turn 6: Seungho]

65
00:02:35,820 --> 00:02:37,060
[Seungho: What's left now?]

66
00:02:37,060 --> 00:02:39,140
[Hyeyeon: The 2 middle spots in the quad]

67
00:02:39,140 --> 00:02:41,270
[Hyeyeon: and the middle spot in the triple room.]

68
00:02:43,320 --> 00:02:49,060
[Hyeyeon & Seungho & Jinwoo—Quad Room]
[Seungho: I'll take the left side
of the 2nd bed in the quad.]

69
00:02:49,060 --> 00:02:50,930
[Seungho: I wanted to get to know]

70
00:02:50,930 --> 00:02:52,530
[Seungho: what Hyeyeon and Jinwoo were thinking.]

71
00:02:52,530 --> 00:02:55,730
[Seungho: Since we cooked together
and spent a lot of time, I felt]

72
00:02:55,730 --> 00:02:57,940
[Seungho: we'd have a great time]

73
00:02:57,940 --> 00:02:59,579
[Seungho: together.]

74
00:02:59,740 --> 00:03:02,140
[Turn 7: Heejin]

75
00:03:00,430 --> 00:03:01,140
Whose turn is it?

76
00:03:01,140 --> 00:03:01,760
-No. 7. -No. 7.

77
00:03:01,760 --> 00:03:02,570
No. 7.

78
00:03:02,410 --> 00:03:03,900
[What's left?]

79
00:03:02,570 --> 00:03:04,110
-What's left? -Bed 3...

80
00:03:03,900 --> 00:03:07,900
[Jinwoo: Bed 3 in the quad
and the middle of the triple?]

81
00:03:07,900 --> 00:03:10,340
[Heejin: Here, here. I pick this spot.]

82
00:03:10,820 --> 00:03:11,140
[Nod]

83
00:03:11,140 --> 00:03:12,380
[Nod]
[Heejin: Oh, wait, wait.]

84
00:03:14,220 --> 00:03:16,090
[Hyeyeon: What's wrong? What are you torn about?]

85
00:03:14,290 --> 00:03:16,090
-What are you torn about? -Are you being indecisive?

86
00:03:16,090 --> 00:03:18,230
[Hyeyeon: Is the triple room tempting?]

87
00:03:18,820 --> 00:03:20,500
[Jinwoo: A bit crowded
makes the triple room way more charming.]

88
00:03:21,460 --> 00:03:23,100
[Laughs]

89
00:03:23,100 --> 00:03:26,230
[Jinwoo: Yongkyu can't stop grinning.]

90
00:03:26,770 --> 00:03:29,440
[Hyeyeon: Let's hear it then.
Where do you want to stay?]

91
00:03:26,900 --> 00:03:29,440
-Where do you want to stay? -Where do you want to stay?

92
00:03:29,440 --> 00:03:31,060
[Yongkyu: Me?]

93
00:03:31,060 --> 00:03:32,660
[Heejin: Both are fine with me.]

94
00:03:32,660 --> 00:03:34,800
[Yongkyu: Want to hear what I think?]

95
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:37,470
[Heejin: Oh... okay, let's hear it.]

96
00:03:37,470 --> 00:03:39,870
[Yongkyu: Honestly, I want to pick this spot.]

97
00:03:41,470 --> 00:03:45,740
[Hyeyeon: If Yongkyu picked the quad,
he would be right next to me.]

98
00:03:45,740 --> 00:03:49,700
[Hyeyeon: And I'd be rooming
with 3 guys.]

99
00:03:49,900 --> 00:03:52,260
[Awkward]

100
00:03:52,260 --> 00:03:56,420
[Hyeyeon: In my head, I was like,
"Please don't pick this room."]

101
00:03:56,420 --> 00:03:58,820
[Yongkyu: Honestly, I want to pick this spot.]

102
00:03:59,350 --> 00:04:00,690
[Heejin: Oh, the quad room?]
[Yongkyu: Yeah, I want to take the quad...]

103
00:04:00,690 --> 00:04:02,020
[Heejin: I'll take bed 3 in the quad.]

104
00:04:02,290 --> 00:04:06,030
[Hyeyeon & Heejin & Seungho & Jinwoo—Quad Room]

105
00:04:07,100 --> 00:04:08,460
[Hyeyeon: It's okay. The triple room's nice, too.]

106
00:04:08,320 --> 00:04:09,520
You say that now, but...

107
00:04:08,460 --> 00:04:12,060
[Chaebe & Yongkyu & Eunchae—Triple Room]
[Yongkyu ends up in the remaining triple room]

108
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:10,470
Yongkyu.

109
00:04:10,470 --> 00:04:11,760
Cozy and crowded.

110
00:04:12,170 --> 00:04:14,570
[Yongkyu: I was sure I'd end up in the quad room.]

111
00:04:14,570 --> 00:04:18,040
[Yongkyu: I'd already cooked dinner with them,
and they were all extroverts I got along with.]

112
00:04:18,040 --> 00:04:20,170
[Yongkyu: Being around them
would feel comfortable.]

113
00:04:20,170 --> 00:04:23,110
[Yongkyu: I thought for sure I'd be in there.]

114
00:04:23,110 --> 00:04:25,140
[Yongkyu: But it turned out like this.]

115
00:04:25,140 --> 00:04:27,650
[Hyeyeon: So the 3 of you
will use the triple room?]

116
00:04:27,650 --> 00:04:30,320
[Chaebe: Yeah.]

117
00:04:30,590 --> 00:04:32,450
[Chaebe: I was thinking of Heejin.]

118
00:04:32,450 --> 00:04:35,920
[Chaebe: Since she picked the quad,
I felt a bit...]

119
00:04:36,100 --> 00:04:38,140
[Disappointed]

120
00:04:38,140 --> 00:04:40,460
[Chaebe: disappointed.]

121
00:04:41,260 --> 00:04:43,670
[Eunchae: I was a bit surprised.]

122
00:04:43,670 --> 00:04:47,940
[Eunchae: Their sleeping habits]

123
00:04:47,940 --> 00:04:51,409
[Eunchae: and the way they live]

124
00:04:51,409 --> 00:04:53,010
[Eunchae: really needed]

125
00:04:53,010 --> 00:04:54,880
[Eunchae: to match.]

126
00:04:54,880 --> 00:04:59,150
[Hyeyeon: Then it's settled.]

127
00:04:59,950 --> 00:05:01,550
[Hyeyeon: I hope everyone makes great roommates.]

128
00:05:02,350 --> 00:05:05,020
[Jinwoo: I thought I was all set]

129
00:05:05,020 --> 00:05:06,350
[Jinwoo: once Seungho ended up right]

130
00:05:06,350 --> 00:05:09,290
[Jinwoo: next to me. Then it hit me]

131
00:05:09,290 --> 00:05:12,490
[Jinwoo: that Hyeyeon
was in the same room too,]

132
00:05:12,490 --> 00:05:15,700
[Jinwoo: and so is Heejin,
who gave a great first impression.]

133
00:05:15,700 --> 00:05:18,100
[Jinwoo: I was really looking forward
to what's ahead.]

134
00:05:18,630 --> 00:05:20,500
[Hyeyeon: The guys I'm interested in—]

135
00:05:20,500 --> 00:05:22,900
[Hyeyeon: I actually didn't want
to share a room with them.]

136
00:05:22,900 --> 00:05:24,510
[Hyeyeon: But Heejin, Heejin,
who was my number one pick,]

137
00:05:24,510 --> 00:05:26,370
[Hyeyeon: was sleeping right next to me.]

138
00:05:26,370 --> 00:05:29,840
[Hyeyeon: And even Seungho
will be in the same room.]

139
00:05:31,450 --> 00:05:33,850
["This is going to be exhausting."]

140
00:05:34,120 --> 00:05:36,250
[Heejin: I only want the person I like]

141
00:05:36,250 --> 00:05:39,450
[Heejin: to see my best, prettiest side.]

142
00:05:39,450 --> 00:05:41,320
[Heejin: I was a bit self-conscious about that.]

143
00:05:41,860 --> 00:05:45,860
[Sujin: I was a bit uneasy
about her sharing a bed with Hyeyeon.]

144
00:05:45,860 --> 00:05:48,530
[Sujin: I would just have]

145
00:05:48,530 --> 00:05:50,740
[Sujin: to visit her often.]

146
00:05:50,780 --> 00:05:53,420
[Roommates decided with different motives]

147
00:05:53,460 --> 00:05:55,500
[Will their feelings for each other change?]

148
00:05:56,540 --> 00:06:00,810
[Jinwoo: It feels like a school field trip.]
[Seungho: Totally.]

149
00:05:59,159 --> 00:05:59,850
Right?

150
00:06:01,180 --> 00:06:04,060
[Chaebe: Can you manage? Let me help.]
[Heejin: I'm good.]

151
00:06:04,060 --> 00:06:06,460
[Chaebe: Are you sure?]
[Heejin: I'll let you know if I need help.]

152
00:06:06,460 --> 00:06:08,070
[Chaebe: Got it.]

153
00:06:08,870 --> 00:06:13,400
[Heejin: Is this that 3-hour patch?]
[Chaebe: Yeah, I think so.]

154
00:06:13,400 --> 00:06:16,340
[Heejin: When I went to Olive Young recently...]
[Chaebe: I bought it yesterday, too.]

155
00:06:16,340 --> 00:06:18,480
[Heejin: I debated getting it,
but ended up passing.]

156
00:06:18,480 --> 00:06:22,210
[Chaebe: Let me help you, though.]
[Heejin: Oh, thanks.]

157
00:06:22,750 --> 00:06:26,750
[Chaebe: Wow, this is heavy.]
[Heejin: These two are a bit heavy.]

158
00:06:27,820 --> 00:06:31,820
[Jinwoo: Careful, it's really going to roll down.]

159
00:06:33,310 --> 00:06:34,230
What's wrong? What happened?

160
00:06:34,230 --> 00:06:35,630
Do you have to carry it up?

161
00:06:38,500 --> 00:06:41,970
[Heejin: Am I strong?]
[Chaebe: Pretty strong.]

162
00:06:41,970 --> 00:06:44,370
[Heejin: Though I'm wobbling a bit.]

163
00:06:50,780 --> 00:06:54,780
[Chaebe carries over Heejin's last suitcase]

164
00:06:55,700 --> 00:06:56,490
Thanks.

165
00:06:56,490 --> 00:06:57,750
Seriously, thank you.

166
00:07:00,110 --> 00:07:01,530
Thank you so much.

167
00:07:04,660 --> 00:07:09,460
[Chaebe: Staying in this room should be fun.]

168
00:07:06,080 --> 00:07:06,830
No, wait...

169
00:07:09,460 --> 00:07:14,270
[Chaebe: How are you going to unpack all this?]
[Heejin: Exactly, that's why I...]

170
00:07:14,270 --> 00:07:19,600
[Heejin: originally wanted the single room,
but things didn't work out that way.]
[Chaebe: True.]

171
00:07:19,870 --> 00:07:23,880
[Chaebe lingers around Heejin,
bummed they aren't roommates]

172
00:07:23,970 --> 00:07:24,670
Hold on.

173
00:07:26,810 --> 00:07:28,950
[Chaebe: Want some help?]
[Hyeyeon: I'm all done.]

174
00:07:28,090 --> 00:07:28,860
Really?

175
00:07:29,750 --> 00:07:32,950
[Heejin dashes out the moment
she hears Hyeyeon's voice]

176
00:07:32,950 --> 00:07:36,420
[Heejin: That looks heavy. Give it to me.]

177
00:07:37,140 --> 00:07:38,270
Wearing a backpack.

178
00:07:38,659 --> 00:07:41,300
[Heavy footsteps]

179
00:07:48,860 --> 00:07:50,580
[Oof.]

180
00:07:51,100 --> 00:07:54,040
[Hyeyeon: I think this would look great on you.]
[Heejin: Really?]

181
00:07:54,040 --> 00:07:56,970
[Hyeyeon: If we go on a date, I'll wear it.]

182
00:07:57,510 --> 00:08:00,180
[Heejin: Should we both wear mint green that day?]
[Hyeyeon: Like a couple look.]

183
00:08:00,180 --> 00:08:05,250
[Heejin: Because you love skirts, right?]
[Hyeyeon: Yeah, you remembered.]

184
00:08:05,250 --> 00:08:12,190
[Heejin: You seem to really love pretty girls.]
[Hyeyeon: Sorry, I can't argue with that.]

185
00:08:12,470 --> 00:08:13,410
Right?

186
00:08:12,720 --> 00:08:15,930
[Sharing a bed together, how
will Heejin and Hyeyeon's relationship unfold?]

187
00:08:18,150 --> 00:08:24,560
[Sujin: Wow, how did you carry that up?
Are you okay?]
[Yongkyu: No.]

188
00:08:24,560 --> 00:08:26,690
[Yongkyu: How are you going to get yours up?]
[Sujin: I have no idea.]

189
00:08:26,690 --> 00:08:30,300
[Yongkyu: Leave it there. I'll get it for you.]
[Sujin: Oh, no, it's fine.]

190
00:08:35,740 --> 00:08:37,380
[Drops it down]

191
00:08:39,360 --> 00:08:44,430
[Yongkyu drops his bag
and heads back to the first floor]

192
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:48,170
[Sujin: I've got this.]
[Yongkyu: Give it here. Let me carry it.]

193
00:08:46,140 --> 00:08:47,010
Outside.

194
00:08:48,170 --> 00:08:51,370
[Sujin: But it's really heavy.
Should we lift it together?]

195
00:08:54,840 --> 00:08:58,040
[Sujin: Wow, so cool, so cool.]

196
00:08:58,040 --> 00:09:01,510
[Sujin: Thank you so much. Careful, watch out.]

197
00:09:01,510 --> 00:09:04,720
[Sujin: You can just drop it right there.
Thanks a million.]

198
00:09:04,720 --> 00:09:05,900
[Yongkyu: This is my room, right?
The single room?]

199
00:09:05,900 --> 00:09:07,540
[Sujin: Yes.]

200
00:09:07,540 --> 00:09:08,580
[Sujin: Yes... wait, what?]

201
00:09:08,160 --> 00:09:08,790
This is my room, right?

202
00:09:08,580 --> 00:09:10,860
[Sujin: Invite you over later? Invite you?]

203
00:09:10,860 --> 00:09:13,790
[Sujin: Ah, thanks a lot.]
[Yongkyu: Sure.]

204
00:09:21,530 --> 00:09:25,270
[Yongkyu: It didn't hit me
during my date with Sujin.]

205
00:09:25,270 --> 00:09:26,600
[Yongkyu: But after the date,]

206
00:09:26,600 --> 00:09:29,270
[Yongkyu: when everyone was chatting together,]

207
00:09:29,270 --> 00:09:31,140
[Yongkyu: I thought, "She seems great."]

208
00:09:31,140 --> 00:09:33,280
[Yongkyu: I'm kind of curious about her.]

209
00:09:34,880 --> 00:09:39,420
[Hyeyeon: Jinwoo, do you
have a lot of zip-up hoodies?]
[Jinwoo: I have a few.]

210
00:09:39,420 --> 00:09:41,820
[Hyeyeon: Can I borrow one?]
[Jinwoo: Sure.]

211
00:09:42,090 --> 00:09:46,890
[Jinwoo: I'm wearing the black one today.]
[Hyeyeon: Then lend me the other one, please!]

212
00:09:44,010 --> 00:09:46,070
-Well then... -Then the other one...

213
00:09:46,890 --> 00:09:49,030
[Jinwoo: First, option No. 1 and...]

214
00:09:49,030 --> 00:09:53,300
[Hyeyeon: Oh, I have a spring color palette.]
[Jinwoo: This one.]

215
00:09:53,300 --> 00:09:54,900
[Hyeyeon: Okay.]

216
00:09:55,170 --> 00:09:56,500
[Jinwoo: I'm wearing this today.]

217
00:09:56,500 --> 00:09:59,440
[Jinwoo: So you can wear whatever tomorrow.]

218
00:09:59,440 --> 00:10:01,840
[The quad room is loud and chaotic
as they share clothes]

219
00:09:59,500 --> 00:10:00,480
Black, black.

220
00:10:13,320 --> 00:10:18,660
[Eunchae: Are people usually this quiet?]

221
00:10:18,660 --> 00:10:22,500
[Yongkyu: Everyone's just tired right now.]

222
00:10:22,500 --> 00:10:28,910
[Chaebe: Do you prefer the top or bottom?]
[Eunchae: I might not reach the top.]

223
00:10:28,910 --> 00:10:32,650
[Chaebe: I'll take the top then.]
[Eunchae: Thanks.]

224
00:10:33,180 --> 00:10:37,450
[The triple room stays quiet
and busy unpacking their bags]

225
00:10:37,450 --> 00:10:41,190
[Eunchae: I'll go change first, then.]

226
00:10:38,060 --> 00:10:40,410
-I'll go change first, then. -Okay.

227
00:10:41,190 --> 00:10:46,260
[Yongkyu: What's that?]
[Chaebe: This? A fan.]

228
00:10:46,260 --> 00:10:47,860
[Chaebe: Just in case.]

229
00:10:47,860 --> 00:10:52,400
[Yongkyu: It's freezing.]
[Chaebe: I didn't expect it to be this cold.]

230
00:10:55,870 --> 00:10:59,870
[Yongkyu: Which side are you sleeping on?]
[Chaebe: Inside.]

231
00:10:59,230 --> 00:11:00,220
Got it.

232
00:11:03,340 --> 00:11:08,420
[Yongkyu: Sleeping by the window must be freezing.]
[Eunchae: I'll just brave the cold then.]

233
00:11:08,420 --> 00:11:13,220
[Yongkyu: It's chilly by the window.
It'll get cold at night.]

234
00:11:13,220 --> 00:11:18,030
[Eunchae: You guys must be warm. I'm jealous.]

235
00:11:15,530 --> 00:11:16,990
-Both sides.-So jealous.

236
00:11:18,030 --> 00:11:21,760
[Yongkyu: Because I run hot anyway.]

237
00:11:21,760 --> 00:11:27,100
[Chaebe: You didn't want to share a bed, right?]
[Yongkyu: No, that's not it. Come on.]

238
00:11:27,070 --> 00:11:28,150
You must be a bit disappointed.

239
00:11:27,370 --> 00:11:32,710
[Joking around helps the triple room trio
break the ice]

240
00:11:28,150 --> 00:11:30,810
-I snore, by the way. -Yeah, a bit disappointed.

241
00:11:31,200 --> 00:11:32,750
Because I snore.

242
00:11:33,240 --> 00:11:38,310
[Heejin & Hyeyeon head downstairs
to do the dishes]

243
00:11:38,480 --> 00:11:40,500
Let's just draw straws to be fair.

244
00:11:38,580 --> 00:11:41,580
[Just now]

245
00:11:40,500 --> 00:11:41,520
-Okay. -Redo.

246
00:11:41,520 --> 00:11:42,950
Numbers 1 and 8 wash together.

247
00:11:41,580 --> 00:11:44,820
[Hyeyeon: Numbers 1 and 8 wash together.]

248
00:11:42,950 --> 00:11:45,480
-Okay, 1 and 8. -Numbers 1 and 8 wash together.

249
00:11:46,120 --> 00:11:47,320
-Curious. -Let's go.

250
00:11:47,630 --> 00:11:48,760
I was number 6 just now.

251
00:11:48,120 --> 00:11:49,460
[Picked number 1]

252
00:11:48,760 --> 00:11:49,740
This is crazy.

253
00:11:49,740 --> 00:11:50,940
Who is it? Who's number 8?

254
00:11:50,940 --> 00:11:54,500
[Picked number 8]

255
00:11:52,240 --> 00:11:53,250
Are you number 8?

256
00:11:53,250 --> 00:11:54,630
I'm number 1.

257
00:11:54,540 --> 00:11:57,660
[Hyeyeon: Want to swap with me?]
[Yongkyu: No way.]

258
00:11:57,700 --> 00:12:00,180
[That settles today's dish duty]

259
00:11:58,460 --> 00:12:00,990
-I don't want to swap. -I swear, I'm losing it.

260
00:12:01,540 --> 00:12:08,480
[Heejin: I'll dump the food waste here first.]
[Hyeyeon: Okay, I'll take care of the dry trash.]

261
00:12:08,480 --> 00:12:15,150
[Heejin: I actually love cleaning up.]
[Hyeyeon: Really? Oh, you do. Time for dishes.]

262
00:12:11,460 --> 00:12:11,860
Yeah.

263
00:12:15,150 --> 00:12:18,090
[Heejin: But when I drew number 1...]
[Hyeyeon: Yeah?]

264
00:12:18,090 --> 00:12:23,960
[Heejin: I literally thought,
"You've got to be kidding me."]
[Hyeyeon: The universe is against me.]

265
00:12:22,510 --> 00:12:23,320
Seriously.

266
00:12:23,960 --> 00:12:30,100
[Heejin: I have zero luck with drawings anyway.]
[Hyeyeon: Well, but]

267
00:12:30,360 --> 00:12:33,570
["At least I got paired up with you. Phew."]

268
00:12:31,970 --> 00:12:33,030
-Is that so? -Phew.

269
00:12:33,570 --> 00:12:37,840
[Heejin: Let me clear those things.]
[Hyeyeon: I'm a dishwashing master.]

270
00:12:37,840 --> 00:12:42,910
[Heejin: Wait up, I need to tie my hair back.]

271
00:12:42,910 --> 00:12:48,250
[Hyeyeon: Showing off your hair-tying skills?]
[Heejin: Just throwing it up quickly.]

272
00:12:51,860 --> 00:12:53,900
[Focused]

273
00:13:01,860 --> 00:13:05,330
[Hyeyeon: Is this fun to you?]
[Heejin: Not at all.]

274
00:13:05,330 --> 00:13:07,200
[Hyeyeon: Really?]

275
00:13:07,200 --> 00:13:12,270
[Hyeyeon: Ditching me already?]
[Heejin: It's pretty boring.]

276
00:13:12,540 --> 00:13:17,080
[The two enjoy a sweet moment
washing dishes together]

277
00:13:17,610 --> 00:13:19,750
[Just then, Sujin walks into the kitchen]

278
00:13:20,010 --> 00:13:24,020
[Heejin: What brings you here?]
[Sujin: Just dropping by.]

279
00:13:24,860 --> 00:13:28,660
[Sujin: When I walked in,
I wanted]

280
00:13:28,660 --> 00:13:30,260
[Sujin: to stay close to her.]

281
00:13:30,260 --> 00:13:32,400
[Sujin: I wanted to talk to her more.]

282
00:13:32,400 --> 00:13:34,540
[Sujin: I wanted to go on a date with her.]

283
00:13:34,540 --> 00:13:35,870
[Sujin: I needed to make my feelings clear.]

284
00:13:35,870 --> 00:13:38,010
[Sujin: I should be more obvious about it.]

285
00:13:38,810 --> 00:13:42,010
[Sujin: Oh! What's going on with us?]

286
00:13:40,850 --> 00:13:41,970
Look at us.

287
00:13:41,970 --> 00:13:43,670
-We're matching! -Exactly!

288
00:13:42,010 --> 00:13:47,620
[Heejin: Oh, we're matching]
[Sujin: Guess I have to help now.]

289
00:13:43,670 --> 00:13:44,910
Need a hand?

290
00:13:44,910 --> 00:13:46,910
What's going on? What's happening?

291
00:13:47,620 --> 00:13:51,350
[Heejin: No need, we'll finish up soon. Together.]

292
00:13:51,350 --> 00:13:52,690
[Heejin: We don't have wet tissue here, right?]

293
00:13:52,690 --> 00:13:58,830
[Sujin: Wet tissue?
I have some in my room.]

294
00:13:54,190 --> 00:13:55,790
Doesn't look like it, right?

295
00:13:58,830 --> 00:14:02,560
[Heejin: Gosh.]

296
00:14:03,630 --> 00:14:08,440
[Sujin: Nothing is even there.
Why are you pouring water?]

297
00:14:08,400 --> 00:14:08,680
No, wait...

298
00:14:08,440 --> 00:14:12,170
[Sujin: He's pouring water on an empty spot.]

299
00:14:12,170 --> 00:14:16,440
[Jinwoo: Just cleaning, cleaning.]
[Sujin: You're just messing around, aren't you?]

300
00:14:15,390 --> 00:14:16,050
Yep.

301
00:14:16,440 --> 00:14:19,650
[Heejin: Thanks for coming to help out.]

302
00:14:18,820 --> 00:14:19,540
Of course.

303
00:14:19,650 --> 00:14:23,120
[Sujin: My single room is way too quiet.]

304
00:14:23,120 --> 00:14:26,850
[Sujin: I have to wash up
and shower alone in my bathrobe.]

305
00:14:26,850 --> 00:14:30,060
[Jinwoo: All by yourself.]
[Sujin: Incredibly lonely.]

306
00:14:30,060 --> 00:14:32,990
[Heejin: I don't even know where to do my hair.]

307
00:14:32,140 --> 00:14:32,900
Exactly.

308
00:14:32,990 --> 00:14:37,000
[Jinwoo: Putting on makeup in the quad room
is going to be hilarious.]

309
00:14:35,730 --> 00:14:36,460
For real.

310
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:41,800
[Sujin: You can come use my single room.
Do your makeup there.]

311
00:14:41,800 --> 00:14:45,810
[Heejin: Really?]
[Sujin: Yeah, I have 2 mirrors—
the bathroom one and the vanity one.]

312
00:14:42,060 --> 00:14:42,860
That's great.

313
00:14:45,800 --> 00:14:47,630
-And the vanity mirror. -Sign me up.

314
00:14:45,810 --> 00:14:49,010
[Hyeyeon: Sign me up.]

315
00:14:47,630 --> 00:14:49,020
-Sign me up. -Come on over.

316
00:14:49,010 --> 00:14:53,810
[Sujin: But you have to check
if my makeup looks okay.]
[Hyeyeon: Of course.]

317
00:14:53,810 --> 00:14:57,820
[Hyeyeon: I'll give it my full effort.]
[Heejin: Sounds like a great deal.]

318
00:15:00,620 --> 00:15:02,980
[Yongkyu: So, has anyone caught your eye yet?]

319
00:15:03,020 --> 00:15:06,980
[Flustered]

320
00:15:03,050 --> 00:15:04,500
-Me? -Yeah.

321
00:15:07,020 --> 00:15:08,860
[Yongkyu: Has anyone? Yeah, there is.]

322
00:15:08,860 --> 00:15:11,800
[Eunchae: Look at you, hesitating.]

323
00:15:10,860 --> 00:15:11,530
Do you?

324
00:15:11,800 --> 00:15:12,870
[Eunchae: I still need to observe more.]

325
00:15:12,870 --> 00:15:16,600
[Eunchae: I literally just got here.]

326
00:15:13,160 --> 00:15:15,620
-I literally just got here. -True.

327
00:15:15,620 --> 00:15:16,380
Me too.

328
00:15:16,380 --> 00:15:18,450
Just first impressions.

329
00:15:16,600 --> 00:15:25,680
[Chaebe: Just first impressions.]
[Yongkyu: Like their looks or the way they talk.]

330
00:15:18,450 --> 00:15:20,850
-First impressions. -First impressions?

331
00:15:27,280 --> 00:15:30,480
[Eunchae: Overall, everyone seems pretty nice.]

332
00:15:31,550 --> 00:15:36,890
[Eunchae: I intentionally kept my expectations low
before coming.]

333
00:15:36,890 --> 00:15:39,560
[Chaebe: Same here.]

334
00:15:39,560 --> 00:15:43,030
[Eunchae: It feels better than coming in
with high hopes.]

335
00:15:40,900 --> 00:15:41,470
Exactly.

336
00:15:43,360 --> 00:15:46,290
[Eunchae: Do you have anyone?]
[Yongkyu: Yeah.]

337
00:15:46,290 --> 00:15:48,430
[Eunchae: How do you think they feel about you?]

338
00:15:48,430 --> 00:15:52,170
[Yongkyu: No idea. That, I don't know.]

339
00:15:48,520 --> 00:15:49,640
-No idea. -That's the most important part.

340
00:15:49,640 --> 00:15:50,970
-Really? -No idea.

341
00:15:52,170 --> 00:15:56,440
[Yongkyu: What about you?]
[Chaebe: Me?]

342
00:15:56,440 --> 00:16:00,170
[Chaebe: I feel like they probably
won't be interested in me.]

343
00:16:00,170 --> 00:16:05,510
[Chaebe: It's less of a crush
and more like, "Oh, they seem cool."]

344
00:16:05,510 --> 00:16:10,320
[Eunchae: Wait, did you join late too?]
[Chaebe: We both did.]

345
00:16:07,860 --> 00:16:10,030
-Same. -We both arrived late.

346
00:16:10,320 --> 00:16:15,390
[Chaebe: Everyone seems so close already.]

347
00:16:12,950 --> 00:16:14,040
-Right. -Yeah.

348
00:16:15,390 --> 00:16:19,390
[Chaebe: So I don't know
how to join the conversation.]
[Yongkyu: It must be awkward arriving late.]

349
00:16:19,390 --> 00:16:25,530
[Eunchae: No wonder you've been so quiet.]

350
00:16:23,510 --> 00:16:24,410
Makes sense.

351
00:16:25,800 --> 00:16:29,000
[Chaebe: Surprisingly,
we were all talking in whispers.]

352
00:16:29,000 --> 00:16:30,870
[Chaebe: It was really nice.]

353
00:16:30,870 --> 00:16:34,880
[Chaebe: Yongkyu kept chatting with me.]

354
00:16:34,880 --> 00:16:39,410
[Chaebe: I didn't feel awkward.]

355
00:16:40,660 --> 00:16:43,820
[Mission] [Stand BI Me]

356
00:16:44,490 --> 00:16:48,760
[Hyeyeon: Let's check it.]
[Sujin: We got a new mission.]

357
00:16:50,360 --> 00:16:52,490
[Heejin: What's wrong?
What does the text say?]

358
00:16:52,490 --> 00:16:56,500
[Sujin: It says to text the name of the person
who left the strongest first impression.]

359
00:16:55,720 --> 00:16:56,370
Really?

360
00:16:56,500 --> 00:17:01,030
[Sujin: We're all sitting right here.
How can we send this now?]

361
00:16:57,750 --> 00:16:59,580
-How can we send this now? -Sorry.

362
00:16:59,580 --> 00:17:00,290
Right?

363
00:17:01,030 --> 00:17:02,370
[Sujin: Let's split up first.]

364
00:17:02,370 --> 00:17:05,569
[Sujin: But we can only pick one person, right?
Not two?]

365
00:17:05,569 --> 00:17:08,240
[Hyeyeon: Does someone
pop into your head right away?]

366
00:17:08,240 --> 00:17:09,839
[Sujin: Yeah.]

367
00:17:09,839 --> 00:17:11,180
[Sujin: Yeah. Oh? No one comes to mind for you?]

368
00:17:11,180 --> 00:17:14,380
[Hyeyeon: Someone did.]

369
00:17:14,380 --> 00:17:17,849
[Hyeyeon: I didn't think of it
as a vote for someone I like.
I took it literally and picked]

370
00:17:17,849 --> 00:17:20,250
[Hyeyeon: the person who left
the strongest first impression on me.]

371
00:17:20,790 --> 00:17:24,790
[Who left the strongest first impression
on Hyeyeon?]

372
00:17:23,230 --> 00:17:25,030
I need to double-check the name.

373
00:17:25,859 --> 00:17:28,800
[Sent]

374
00:17:29,040 --> 00:17:33,020
[Heejin: I just focused on the question itself—]

375
00:17:33,020 --> 00:17:35,260
[Heejin: The person who left the strongest
first impression on me.]

376
00:17:35,260 --> 00:17:38,620
[Heejin: I haven't fully made up my mind yet.]

377
00:17:38,620 --> 00:17:44,620
[Heejin: Honestly, everyone was great.
They were all nice people.]

378
00:17:45,140 --> 00:17:48,820
[Sujin: After dinner, we had time to talk]

379
00:17:48,820 --> 00:17:50,300
[Sujin: to each other.]

380
00:17:50,300 --> 00:17:54,460
[Sujin: I felt like we really clicked.]

381
00:17:59,360 --> 00:18:02,780
[Seungho: I was torn between 2 people.]

382
00:18:02,780 --> 00:18:07,580
[Seungho: Because we kept ending up together,
and it was fun every time.]

383
00:18:07,580 --> 00:18:12,380
[Seungho: And they took good care of me.]

384
00:18:12,620 --> 00:18:14,860
[Peeking]

385
00:18:16,020 --> 00:18:17,100
[Ah, I'm exhausted.]

386
00:18:17,100 --> 00:18:21,340
[Jinwoo: Did you send it?]
[Seungho: Yeah, I'm doing it now.]

387
00:18:21,360 --> 00:18:23,230
[Jinwoo: There's really nothing to overthink.]

388
00:18:23,230 --> 00:18:25,370
[Jinwoo: I saw everyone hesitating,]

389
00:18:25,370 --> 00:18:26,970
[Jinwoo: so I just pretended to think it over, too.]

390
00:18:27,500 --> 00:18:30,170
[Jinwoo: I naturally wrote down
this person's name.]

391
00:18:31,140 --> 00:18:36,060
[The triple room receives the mission text, too]

392
00:18:33,650 --> 00:18:35,510
But can you remember the names?

393
00:18:36,310 --> 00:18:41,380
[Who left the strongest first impression?]

394
00:18:41,820 --> 00:18:45,820
[Yongkyu: The more we talked and interacted,]

395
00:18:45,820 --> 00:18:47,690
[Yongkyu: the more curious I became about them]

396
00:18:47,690 --> 00:18:49,560
[Yongkyu: and wanted to get to know them.]

397
00:18:49,820 --> 00:18:52,230
[Chaebe: Honestly, I struggled with this.]

398
00:18:52,230 --> 00:18:57,300
[Chaebe: Should I pick a guy or a girl?]

399
00:18:57,300 --> 00:19:03,170
[Chaebe: But since it asked
for the first impression...]

400
00:19:03,440 --> 00:19:07,170
[Eunchae: "Please vote for the person
who left the strongest first impression."]

401
00:19:07,170 --> 00:19:08,780
[Eunchae: That's how it went.]

402
00:19:08,780 --> 00:19:14,650
[Eunchae: I found them the most attractive,
so I voted for them.]

403
00:19:14,920 --> 00:19:19,990
[Who was Eunchae interested in?]

404
00:19:19,990 --> 00:19:22,540
[Yongkyu: Did you send it?]
[Chaebe: Yeah.] [Nod]

405
00:19:22,540 --> 00:19:28,260
[Yongkyu: Why do you look so unsatisfied?]

406
00:19:30,130 --> 00:19:33,100
[Eunchae: Already? Is this right?]

407
00:19:30,590 --> 00:19:32,850
-Is this right? -Can't make up your mind?

408
00:19:33,100 --> 00:19:37,660
[Yongkyu: That's just how it is.
You know, when you first meet.]
[Chaebe: Exactly, first impressions.]

409
00:19:37,660 --> 00:19:39,270
[Yongkyu: Yeah, first impressions.]

410
00:19:39,270 --> 00:19:44,340
[Yongkyu: Are you overthinking?
Are you planning the wedding already?]

411
00:19:43,550 --> 00:19:44,440
No, it's just...

412
00:19:44,340 --> 00:19:47,810
[Eunchae: If it's just about first impressions,
I can definitely name someone.]

413
00:19:47,810 --> 00:19:52,080
[Eunchae: But actually sending it
to one person felt kind of...]

414
00:19:52,080 --> 00:19:56,350
[Yongkyu: Since you're here, finding someone
close to your ideal type is already not bad.]

415
00:19:57,020 --> 00:19:59,340
[Click]

416
00:19:59,340 --> 00:20:01,580
[Click] [Hyeyeon: Hey, everyone.]

417
00:20:01,580 --> 00:20:07,830
[Jinwoo: Hey guys, we are here to hang out.]
[Seungho: Hey, we were bored,
so we finished everything and came over.]

418
00:20:02,200 --> 00:20:04,530
-Hey, we are here to hang out. -We're here.

419
00:20:05,230 --> 00:20:07,460
-Can we come in? -We finished our chores.

420
00:20:07,460 --> 00:20:08,810
What are you guys talking about?

421
00:20:07,830 --> 00:20:11,830
[They gather in the triple room one by one]

422
00:20:09,720 --> 00:20:11,880
-Hey there. -Hello.

423
00:20:13,060 --> 00:20:15,300
[Heejin: We thought you'd be bored,
so we came to visit.]

424
00:20:14,580 --> 00:20:15,250
Yeah.

425
00:20:15,270 --> 00:20:16,780
We thought you'd be bored.

426
00:20:16,780 --> 00:20:18,380
-We were chatting. -Welcome.

427
00:20:17,300 --> 00:20:22,220
[The first impression results are in]

428
00:20:18,380 --> 00:20:19,370
What is it?

429
00:20:19,370 --> 00:20:20,690
Now I'm kind of scared to look.

430
00:20:20,690 --> 00:20:22,110
-I can't look. -Same here.

431
00:20:22,110 --> 00:20:24,150
Hold on, let me turn down
my screen brightness first.

432
00:20:22,780 --> 00:20:25,450
[Checking their results]

433
00:20:27,900 --> 00:20:29,900
[Seungho: Oh wow, this is interesting.]

434
00:20:29,900 --> 00:20:34,250
[Jinwoo: Right? This is getting juicy.]

435
00:20:30,870 --> 00:20:33,000
-This is juicy. -So that's how it went.

436
00:20:35,590 --> 00:20:38,530
[To Hyeyeon: A girl chose you.]

437
00:20:38,530 --> 00:20:42,000
[Hyeyeon: A girl voted for me.]

438
00:20:42,000 --> 00:20:43,860
[Hyeyeon: For some reason, I felt like]

439
00:20:43,860 --> 00:20:47,870
[Hyeyeon: it was either Sujin or Heejin.]

440
00:20:47,870 --> 00:20:51,870
[Hyeyeon: I was actually hoping it'd be Sujin.]

441
00:20:51,870 --> 00:20:54,270
[Hyeyeon: rather than Heejin.]

442
00:20:55,880 --> 00:21:01,750
[Is it Sujin, like Hyeyeon hopes?
Or Heejin, who shared her very first moment?]

443
00:21:01,750 --> 00:21:04,150
[Heejin chose Hyeyeon]

444
00:21:04,150 --> 00:21:07,890
[Heejin: She left a strong impression on me.]

445
00:21:07,890 --> 00:21:10,820
[Heejin: While spending time with her
every now and then,]

446
00:21:11,090 --> 00:21:17,760
[Heejin: I felt her kindness.
She seemed like a wonderful person.]

447
00:21:18,300 --> 00:21:21,500
[To Yongkyu: A girl chose you.]

448
00:21:21,770 --> 00:21:25,240
[Yongkyu: A girl picked me today.]

449
00:21:25,240 --> 00:21:26,570
[Yongkyu: I had no idea who it was.]

450
