681
00:33:47,260 --> 00:33:50,120
-Looks like it. -Let me pass you the utensils first.

682
00:33:50,660 --> 00:33:52,300
Like this, like this.

683
00:33:53,680 --> 00:33:57,950
[Jinwoo: Try it first. You wanted to eat it, right?]
[Seungho: Yeah, I want some bacon.]

684
00:33:57,790 --> 00:33:59,090
Give it a try.

685
00:33:59,090 --> 00:34:00,570
I'll have a tomato.

686
00:34:05,160 --> 00:34:08,900
[Seungho: I want to eat elegantly,
but I just can't pull it off.]

687
00:34:08,900 --> 00:34:12,900
[Jinwoo: You want to eat elegantly?]

688
00:34:13,900 --> 00:34:15,400
Aren't you drinking a bit too fast?

689
00:34:14,500 --> 00:34:21,100
[The more awkward it gets, the faster he drinks]

690
00:34:15,400 --> 00:34:16,290
Slow down.

691
00:34:16,290 --> 00:34:18,219
-Sip it slowly. -I'm totally fine.

692
00:34:22,980 --> 00:34:26,060
[This is delicious.]

693
00:34:26,060 --> 00:34:29,719
[Seungho: How do you feel?
Did you think I'd choose you?]

694
00:34:29,719 --> 00:34:31,580
[Jinwoo: Yeah.]
[Seungho: Really?]

695
00:34:31,580 --> 00:34:36,659
[Jinwoo: It's not that I think highly of myself,
but I was a little...]

696
00:34:37,460 --> 00:34:42,800
[Jinwoo: I got that text saying the person
who picked me was a guy.]

697
00:34:44,929 --> 00:34:54,010
[Jinwoo: But since a guy picked me,
I thought about who it could be.]

698
00:34:50,699 --> 00:34:51,580
Who is it?

699
00:34:52,830 --> 00:34:54,590
It's only me, don't you think?

700
00:34:54,540 --> 00:34:59,880
[Jinwoo: My first date was also with Seungho.]

701
00:34:59,880 --> 00:35:05,220
[Jinwoo: Even though I met Yongkyu
for the first time...]

702
00:35:05,220 --> 00:35:09,760
[Jinwoo: We barely talked, so it's unlikely
he picked me.]

703
00:35:09,760 --> 00:35:14,290
[Jinwoo: And I just met Chaebe
not long ago either.]

704
00:35:14,290 --> 00:35:21,500
[Jinwoo: So it had to be Seungho. I figured it out.]

705
00:35:24,170 --> 00:35:27,640
[Jinwoo: And sure enough, you did invite me.]

706
00:35:28,210 --> 00:35:30,070
That's pretty straightforward.

707
00:35:31,640 --> 00:35:32,980
[Jinwoo: Actually, I don't really remember.]

708
00:35:32,980 --> 00:35:35,650
[Jinwoo: Whether I was the one
who suggested the toast first...]

709
00:35:35,650 --> 00:35:38,580
[Jinwoo: or if Seungho was the one
who clinked glasses with me first.]

710
00:35:38,580 --> 00:35:40,990
[Jinwoo: I don't remember clearly, but
it definitely happened fast.]

711
00:35:40,990 --> 00:35:43,920
[Jinwoo: The atmosphere was really great,
as expected.]

712
00:35:43,920 --> 00:35:47,930
[Jinwoo: Topics we don't usually get to
talk about...]

713
00:35:47,930 --> 00:35:53,270
[Jinwoo: We could talk freely in the secret room.
It felt really good.]

714
00:35:55,400 --> 00:35:58,870
[Seungho: I was a bit flustered at the time.
I do like being the center of attention though.]

715
00:35:58,870 --> 00:36:00,600
[Seungho: But all of a sudden...]

716
00:36:00,600 --> 00:36:02,340
[Jinwoo: You became the center of attention
all of a sudden?]

717
00:36:02,340 --> 00:36:06,610
[Seungho: So I was really flustered
at that moment.]

718
00:36:06,610 --> 00:36:10,880
[Jinwoo: You said you were torn
between two people, right?]

719
00:36:10,480 --> 00:36:11,120
Right.

720
00:36:10,880 --> 00:36:16,220
[Jinwoo: That's me and...]
[Seungho: Hyeyeon.]

721
00:36:13,670 --> 00:36:15,220
-Hyeyeon. -Hyeyeon.

722
00:36:16,220 --> 00:36:19,690
[Seungho: And you two were both in that room.]
[Jinwoo: Right?]

723
00:36:19,690 --> 00:36:22,630
[Seungho: So I just went straight to that room.]

724
00:36:22,630 --> 00:36:27,430
[Seungho: And the person with
the strongest first impression...]

725
00:36:26,310 --> 00:36:27,490
Out of the two...

726
00:36:27,490 --> 00:36:29,210
The other one was Jinwoo.

727
00:36:27,970 --> 00:36:30,370
["...was Jinwoo"]

728
00:36:30,500 --> 00:36:34,640
[Jinwoo: Good thing I'm the first date.]

729
00:36:35,220 --> 00:36:38,340
[Seungho: I honestly didn't think many people
would pick me.]

730
00:36:37,480 --> 00:36:38,270
Really?

731
00:36:38,340 --> 00:36:42,650
[Seungho: I'm not good with words,
and I look like a kid...]

732
00:36:42,650 --> 00:36:47,190
[Seungho: So I thought everyone would just see me
as a little brother.]

733
00:36:47,190 --> 00:36:53,330
[Jinwoo: You don't look that much like a kid.
No one would pick you for that reason anyway.]

734
00:36:57,060 --> 00:37:01,600
[Seungho: Jinwoo expressed interest in me
multiple times.]

735
00:37:01,600 --> 00:37:03,470
[Seungho: Rather than pretending
not to be interested...]

736
00:37:03,470 --> 00:37:06,410
[Seungho: I prefer people who actively
come to me like this.]

737
00:37:06,410 --> 00:37:09,080
[Seungho: I already liked him to begin with...]

738
00:37:09,080 --> 00:37:12,280
[Seungho: but my feelings grew
even more after that.]

739
00:37:14,150 --> 00:37:20,820
[Seungho: If I had picked someone else,
how would you have felt?]

740
00:37:21,240 --> 00:37:24,110
Something like that, probably.

741
00:37:25,090 --> 00:37:27,760
[Jinwoo: If it was a girl, I'd understand.]

742
00:37:27,760 --> 00:37:33,100
[Jinwoo: But if it was a guy, I wouldn't be
too disappointed.]

743
00:37:33,100 --> 00:37:38,440
[Jinwoo: I'd just be a little curious,
that's all.]

744
00:37:41,910 --> 00:37:45,510
[Jinwoo: I'm really curious who picked Seungho.]

745
00:37:45,510 --> 00:37:49,120
[Seungho: I'm curious too. They didn't specify
who it was.]

746
00:37:48,070 --> 00:37:48,930
Yeah.

747
00:37:49,120 --> 00:37:55,520
[Jinwoo: I don't know the exact number either.
If there were a lot of people...]

748
00:37:55,520 --> 00:37:57,920
[Seungho: What if there were a lot?]

749
00:37:57,920 --> 00:38:00,330
[Jinwoo: Then the person sitting here should feel
pretty honored, right?]

750
00:38:00,330 --> 00:38:04,860
[Jinwoo: That might be related to
the first date, but still...]

751
00:38:04,860 --> 00:38:12,340
[Jinwoo: Among those who picked Seungho...
[Seungho: It's not that many.]

752
00:38:10,100 --> 00:38:11,020
Still though.

753
00:38:14,740 --> 00:38:16,870
[Seungho: No one would pick me now, right?
Since I'm already on a date?]

754
00:38:16,870 --> 00:38:19,010
[Jinwoo: No, no. You never know.]

755
00:38:19,010 --> 00:38:21,150
[Jinwoo: Could be someone with
a strong competitive streak.]

756
00:38:21,150 --> 00:38:23,280
[Jinwoo: Or someone who wants to win you over.]

757
00:38:23,280 --> 00:38:25,810
[Seungho: That's interesting. That would be fun.]

758
00:38:25,810 --> 00:38:28,350
[Jinwoo: Right? It's exciting. Feels like
the dopamine's spiking.]

759
00:38:28,350 --> 00:38:32,750
[Seungho: I'm the one in question here...]

760
00:38:32,750 --> 00:38:37,160
[Jinwoo: ...but will he get taken away,
or will I be able to keep him?]

761
00:38:37,960 --> 00:38:41,430
[Jinwoo: We're not gonna get too drunk, are we?]
[Seungho: It's fine.]

762
00:38:41,430 --> 00:38:43,840
[Jinwoo: Well, nothing we can do about it, right?]
[Seungho: It is the first day after all.]

763
00:38:42,820 --> 00:38:43,860
Right. It is the first day.

764
00:38:43,840 --> 00:38:47,840
[Jinwoo: Didn't you want to drink anyway?]
[Seungho: When you put it that way...]

765
00:38:47,840 --> 00:38:49,570
[Seungho: Actually, I don't really like
drinking that much.]

766
00:38:49,570 --> 00:38:51,310
[Jinwoo: Me neither.]

767
00:38:51,310 --> 00:38:53,360
[Seungho: I just like the vibe
of drinking together.]

768
00:38:53,360 --> 00:38:55,420
[Jinwoo: Same here.]

769
00:38:55,420 --> 00:38:59,500
[Seungho: I always go along,
but I don't drink much...]

770
00:38:58,310 --> 00:38:59,380
Yeah, yeah.

771
00:39:01,190 --> 00:39:05,990
["Because today's a special day"]

772
00:39:04,350 --> 00:39:05,880
Because it's a special day.

773
00:39:06,190 --> 00:39:07,170
I wonder what everyone else is doing.

774
00:39:07,170 --> 00:39:08,690
Right? No idea what they're up to.

775
00:39:07,500 --> 00:39:13,100
[While the two are having a special night,
what are the other members doing?]

776
00:39:08,690 --> 00:39:09,240
I'm kinda curious.

777
00:39:09,240 --> 00:39:10,900
They're probably having fun.

778
00:39:12,610 --> 00:39:13,860
You're pretty confident.

779
00:39:13,860 --> 00:39:18,420
[Soju? Or Somaek? Soju.]

780
00:39:20,260 --> 00:39:25,210
[Chaebe: But everyone got quite a few votes
for first impressions, right?]

781
00:39:25,210 --> 00:39:27,880
[Eunchae: It already feels like a funeral
parlor in here.]

782
00:39:27,880 --> 00:39:31,080
[Sujin: Didn't you see the memorial table
set up here?]

783
00:39:29,800 --> 00:39:30,850
Oh, come on.

784
00:39:31,080 --> 00:39:34,020
[Chaebe: This isn't for me, is it?
This memorial table?]

785
00:39:32,500 --> 00:39:33,770
No, seriously.

786
00:39:34,020 --> 00:39:36,960
[Heejin: It is the first day though.]

787
00:39:36,960 --> 00:39:44,430
[Heejin: Honestly, things haven't been going
smoothly since day one.]

788
00:39:44,430 --> 00:39:50,300
[Sujin: But those two seem to be doing
well though. The two in the secret room?]

789
00:39:46,760 --> 00:39:48,630
-Those two in the secret room. -Secret room.

790
00:39:48,630 --> 00:39:49,420
No way.

791
00:39:51,100 --> 00:39:54,840
[Heejin: So if the person I like...]

792
00:39:54,840 --> 00:39:57,510
[Heejin: doesn't like me, but someone else
likes him instead.]

793
00:39:57,510 --> 00:40:00,180
[Heejin: If it comes to that,
would you fight for him?]

794
00:40:00,180 --> 00:40:03,120
[Sujin: I would.]
[Chaebe: Really?]

795
00:40:02,310 --> 00:40:03,010
Yeah, I would.

796
00:40:03,010 --> 00:40:04,590
-That's so cool. -I'd go straight for it.

797
00:40:03,120 --> 00:40:04,180
[Sujin: I'd go straight for it.]

798
00:40:04,180 --> 00:40:07,390
[Chaebe: But what if he doesn't like me?]

799
00:40:06,820 --> 00:40:07,440
Even then.

800
00:40:07,390 --> 00:40:12,460
[Sujin: Even if he doesn't like me, I'd still
keep going. But if he says...]

801
00:40:09,690 --> 00:40:11,820
Wow, you're totally the head-on type.

802
00:40:12,460 --> 00:40:17,530
[Sujin: "I feel a bit uncomfortable" or
"Please don't," then I'd say "Got it."]

803
00:40:17,530 --> 00:40:20,200
[Yongkyu: It seems like you'd rather
meet someone you like.]

804
00:40:20,200 --> 00:40:22,870
[Chaebe: Rather than someone who likes you.]

805
00:40:22,870 --> 00:40:28,740
[Sujin: That would be great too, but here,
I need to like the person first.]

806
00:40:27,850 --> 00:40:29,540
That's the only way things can develop. Exactly.

807
00:40:29,540 --> 00:40:33,280
[Sujin: And I'm confident I can make him
like me more and more.]

808
00:40:33,280 --> 00:40:36,220
[Chaebe: You're totally a girlboss.]

809
00:40:36,220 --> 00:40:40,220
[Yongkyu: You need that kind of mindset.
That mindset.]

810
00:40:36,580 --> 00:40:37,760
You need that kind of mindset.

811
00:40:37,760 --> 00:40:40,090
She's got hidden depth. A total girlboss.

812
00:40:40,220 --> 00:40:42,620
[Yongkyu: We need to have that
"we can do it" mindset.]

813
00:40:42,000 --> 00:40:42,680
Impressive.

814
00:40:42,620 --> 00:40:44,490
[Sujin: So if I'm here...]

815
00:40:44,490 --> 00:40:49,560
[Sujin: Let's say I like Eunchae, but
Eunchae likes Chaebe.]

816
00:40:49,560 --> 00:40:50,630
[Sujin: And you two are developing really well.]

817
00:40:50,630 --> 00:40:54,630
[Sujin: Then I'd go to Eunchae and tell her,
"I have feelings for you."]

818
00:40:54,630 --> 00:40:58,900
[Sujin: "Eunchae, would you give me a chance?"]

819
00:40:58,900 --> 00:41:01,570
[Sujin: "Are you interested in going on a date
with me?" That's what I'd say.]

820
00:41:01,750 --> 00:41:02,390
Wow.

821
00:41:03,300 --> 00:41:05,640
[Sujin: At least we should talk, so we
don't regret it later.]

822
00:41:05,340 --> 00:41:07,260
-That's really how it should be here. -Exactly.

823
00:41:05,640 --> 00:41:07,980
[Chaebe: That's really how it should be here.]

824
00:41:07,260 --> 00:41:09,990
-Since we're here, we have to give it our all. -Right.

825
00:41:08,180 --> 00:41:11,940
[Heejin: Since we're here, we have to give it
our all so we don't regret it.]

826
00:41:09,990 --> 00:41:10,460
-So we don't regret it. -If we're here...

827
00:41:10,460 --> 00:41:11,940
Of course we give it our all.

828
00:41:11,940 --> 00:41:13,940
[Sujin: Chaebe gives off the vibe of "Should I
make a move or not?"]

829
00:41:12,040 --> 00:41:13,340
Chaebe gives off the vibe of "Should I make
a move or not?"

830
00:41:13,340 --> 00:41:15,120
Like, "Should I go all in or not?"
That kind of feeling.

831
00:41:13,940 --> 00:41:15,940
[Sujin: Like, "Should I go all in or not?"
That kind of feeling.]

832
00:41:15,950 --> 00:41:19,690
[Heejin: What about Eunchae? What type are you?]

833
00:41:17,640 --> 00:41:18,330
Me?

834
00:41:19,950 --> 00:41:24,490
[Eunchae: Even if I have someone I like...]

835
00:41:24,490 --> 00:41:26,090
[Eunchae: I do take initiative...]

836
00:41:26,090 --> 00:41:29,830
[Eunchae: but I don't show it too obviously
from the start.]

837
00:41:29,830 --> 00:41:33,700
[Eunchae: And I'm just not that type of person.]

838
00:41:34,460 --> 00:41:38,220
[Sujin: Then if Eunchae likes someone,
let's say Person A...]

839
00:41:38,220 --> 00:41:41,980
[Sujin: but Person A is getting along really well
with someone else...]

840
00:41:41,980 --> 00:41:45,780
[Sujin: and keeps appearing
right in front of you.]

841
00:41:43,380 --> 00:41:45,780
Ugh, that's so painful.

842
00:41:45,780 --> 00:41:57,180
[Eunchae: If that's the case, once I confirm that
he's really not interested in me...]

843
00:41:57,180 --> 00:41:59,190
[Eunchae: I wouldn't even start.]

844
00:42:00,260 --> 00:42:04,530
[Eunchae: Once I'm sure he's not
interested in me...]

845
00:42:04,530 --> 00:42:07,730
[Eunchae: I'm the type who won't even try.]

846
00:42:07,730 --> 00:42:11,470
[Eunchae: Why put myself through that?
That's just my mindset.]

847
00:42:11,470 --> 00:42:16,280
[Chaebe: I'm pretty similar to Eunchae.]

848
00:42:12,660 --> 00:42:13,260
Really?

849
00:42:13,260 --> 00:42:14,460
Are you gonna jump in?

850
00:42:15,160 --> 00:42:19,260
-If he's not interested in me... -Thanks.

851
00:42:16,280 --> 00:42:22,410
[Chaebe: If he's not interested in me,
I'm too scared to approach.]

852
00:42:19,930 --> 00:42:22,590
-I'm too scared to approach. -You've had yours?

853
00:42:22,980 --> 00:42:24,900
Let's clink glasses.

854
00:42:25,350 --> 00:42:27,550
-Okay, cheers. -Cheers.

855
00:42:25,660 --> 00:42:28,300
[Cheers~]

856
00:42:28,300 --> 00:42:30,740
[Cheers~]

857
00:42:30,780 --> 00:42:36,030
[Chaebe: While we were drinking and
chatting slowly downstairs,]

858
00:42:36,030 --> 00:42:41,900
[Chaebe: it felt really comfortable. I thought
it was great in that setting.]

859
00:42:41,900 --> 00:42:47,510
[Chaebe: It felt like we broke the ice,
so it was really nice.]

860
00:42:47,770 --> 00:42:49,380
[Sujin: What about Yongkyu? What would you do?
Would you jump in?]

861
00:42:49,380 --> 00:42:53,060
[Yongkyu: As for me, I wouldn't go
as far as jumping in.]

862
00:42:49,580 --> 00:42:50,970
-As for me... -Jump in?

863
00:42:53,060 --> 00:42:55,550
[Yongkyu: If I liked someone, I'd probably
test the waters a few times.]

864
00:42:55,550 --> 00:42:56,550
-Like how? -You'd do that?

865
00:42:55,550 --> 00:42:56,550
[Oh, like how?]

866
00:42:57,100 --> 00:42:59,980
[Smack!]

867
00:42:57,480 --> 00:42:59,360
-How? -Ask "How do you see me?" directly?

868
00:42:59,360 --> 00:43:02,450
-I wouldn't do that. -What would you do?

869
00:43:00,020 --> 00:43:04,060
[Yongkyu: Of course I wouldn't be that direct.]

870
00:43:04,060 --> 00:43:10,200
[Yongkyu: I'd probably show my interest.]
[Heejin: Would you be proactive?]

871
00:43:10,200 --> 00:43:13,670
[Yongkyu: By my standards, I'd say yes.]

872
00:43:13,670 --> 00:43:18,200
[Sujin: Heejin, what would you do?]

873
00:43:16,590 --> 00:43:17,580
But I think...

874
00:43:18,200 --> 00:43:26,210
[Heejin: If the other person doesn't like me,
I'd hold back a little.]

875
00:43:22,450 --> 00:43:24,310
-I'd hold back a little. -Really?

876
00:43:24,520 --> 00:43:26,090
-Wow. -Probably like that.

877
00:43:26,210 --> 00:43:32,890
[Heejin: I need clear signal to take actions.]

878
00:43:29,070 --> 00:43:32,280
-To take actions. -Right, exactly.

879
00:43:33,690 --> 00:43:36,890
[Sujin: I've been staying by her side,
or quietly waiting for her.]

880
00:43:36,890 --> 00:43:40,090
[Sujin: And when everyone was asking questions,]

881
00:43:40,090 --> 00:43:41,960
[Sujin: I looked at Heejin first.]

882
00:43:41,960 --> 00:43:43,830
[Sujin: I asked her first.]

883
00:43:43,830 --> 00:43:48,370
[Sujin: I'm just not sure if she
noticed it or not.]

884
00:43:49,170 --> 00:43:53,970
[While everyone was talking together...
Did Heejin sense Sujin's feelings?]

885
00:43:54,240 --> 00:43:59,040
[Through the exchanges on the first night,
things are slowly heating up.]

886
00:43:59,040 --> 00:44:02,250
[Jinwoo: Wine!]

887
00:43:59,920 --> 00:44:00,740
[Nice!]

888
00:44:06,250 --> 00:44:11,060
[Jinwoo: Thanks to you, I can end the first day
on a good note.]

889
00:44:11,320 --> 00:44:12,980
["Thanks to Seungho"]

890
00:44:12,980 --> 00:44:18,380
[Seungho: Is it okay to say "thanks to you"?]
[Jinwoo: Why? It's thanks to Seungho.]

891
00:44:16,950 --> 00:44:17,670
I see.

892
00:44:18,380 --> 00:44:20,940
[Jinwoo: And we had good food too.]
[Seungho: That's true. We do get along well.]

893
00:44:20,520 --> 00:44:22,030
Right. We get along well.

894
00:44:21,200 --> 00:44:23,870
["Because we get along well"]

895
00:44:23,870 --> 00:44:31,780
[Seungho: You're considerate, and you're good
at starting conversations.]

896
00:44:34,500 --> 00:44:38,520
[Seungho: But it seems like you're not just
like that with me.]

897
00:44:38,520 --> 00:44:42,550
[Seungho: You're like that with everyone,
so I'm a little confused.]

898
00:44:40,890 --> 00:44:41,820
Really?

899
00:44:44,300 --> 00:44:47,820
[Seungho: You know what I mean, right?]
[Jinwoo: Hmm...]

900
00:44:51,380 --> 00:44:54,480
[Jinwoo: I don't mean anything special by it.]

901
00:44:54,480 --> 00:44:57,580
[Jinwoo: It's just that it was the first day and
a little awkward, so I was like that.]

902
00:44:57,620 --> 00:44:59,780
[Hmm...]

903
00:44:59,780 --> 00:45:06,340
[Jinwoo: The more I like someone, the more
flustered I get around them.]

904
00:45:09,290 --> 00:45:12,540
[Seungho: How old do I look to you?
Your first impression.]

905
00:45:12,540 --> 00:45:13,560
First impression?

906
00:45:13,560 --> 00:45:18,900
[Jinwoo: Honestly, you look really young.]
[Seungho: I know everyone thinks I look young.]

907
00:45:17,840 --> 00:45:18,640
Right, right.

908
00:45:18,900 --> 00:45:21,570
[Jinwoo: You want me to guess your exact age?]

909
00:45:21,570 --> 00:45:24,860
[Jinwoo: But honestly, you kind of
gave yourself away earlier.]

910
00:45:24,900 --> 00:45:26,180
[You mean it?]

911
00:45:26,180 --> 00:45:28,380
[License?] [Driver's license.]

912
00:45:28,380 --> 00:45:31,980
[Jinwoo: You said you got it at 19.
You told me that in the car earlier.]

913
00:45:31,980 --> 00:45:35,180
[Seungho: I also told you
how long I've been driving.]

914
00:45:35,180 --> 00:45:39,180
[Jinwoo: So I did a little math.]
[Seungho: That was a lie.]

915
00:45:36,790 --> 00:45:37,450
Because...

916
00:45:39,180 --> 00:45:42,390
[Jinwoo: A lie?]
[Seungho: The driver's license part was true.]

917
00:45:42,390 --> 00:45:47,730
[Seungho: But telling you how long I've had
my license would give away my age.]

918
00:45:44,140 --> 00:45:44,540
Right.

919
00:45:46,400 --> 00:45:47,760
Right, right.

920
00:45:47,730 --> 00:45:51,460
[Seungho: So I lied. I had no choice.]
[Jinwoo: Ah, really?]

921
00:45:51,460 --> 00:45:52,530
[Seungho: You can't blame me for that though.]

922
00:45:52,530 --> 00:45:56,540
[Jinwoo: Of course not.
You were just following the rules.]

923
00:45:56,270 --> 00:45:56,530
Yes.

924
00:45:56,540 --> 00:46:00,270
[Jinwoo: I thought you forgot what you told me
when you said that.]

925
00:46:00,270 --> 00:46:03,480
[Jinwoo: There were other people around,
so when I heard that, I was like, "Huh?"]

926
00:46:03,480 --> 00:46:08,550
[Seungho: No. That was all part of my plan.]
[Jinwoo: You planned it all out.]

927
00:46:04,150 --> 00:46:04,980
-No. -Really?

928
00:46:08,550 --> 00:46:10,680
[Seungho: So how old do you think I am?]

929
00:46:16,020 --> 00:46:24,830
[Jinwoo: 22? 23? Somewhere around that.]

930
00:46:24,830 --> 00:46:29,640
[Seungho: OK, I got it.]

931
00:46:25,760 --> 00:46:26,710
OK, OK, OK.

932
00:46:33,110 --> 00:46:37,640
[Jinwoo: But the way
you call me hyung so naturally]

933
00:46:37,640 --> 00:46:40,580
[Jinwoo: makes you seem younger than I thought.]

934
00:46:40,580 --> 00:46:47,790
[Seungho: But I feel like you already know
I'm younger than you.]

935
00:46:47,080 --> 00:46:47,340
Yes.

936
00:46:47,740 --> 00:46:51,060
-Yeah. -So I just went ahead and called you hyung.

937
00:46:47,790 --> 00:46:52,590
[Seungho: So I just went ahead
and called you hyung.]

938
00:46:53,130 --> 00:47:00,070
[Jinwoo: Are you okay
with dating someone older than you?]

939
00:47:00,070 --> 00:47:03,800
[Seungho: For now,
I think I'd only date someone older.]

940
00:47:03,800 --> 00:47:07,270
[Seungho: It didn't matter to me before.]

941
00:47:07,270 --> 00:47:10,480
[Seungho: But now, I'm not into younger ones.]
[Jinwoo: Oh, really?]

942
00:47:09,390 --> 00:47:10,420
Normally.

943
00:47:10,480 --> 00:47:13,410
[Jinwoo: I'm actually really into younger people.]

944
00:47:13,410 --> 00:47:15,810
[Jinwoo: How old do you think I am? Take a guess.]

945
00:47:15,810 --> 00:47:21,690
[Seungho: 25? 26?]

946
00:47:22,220 --> 00:47:24,620
[Seungho: Am I right?]
[Jinwoo: Maybe, maybe not.]

947
00:47:24,620 --> 00:47:27,030
[Seungho: I think I got it right.]
[Jinwoo: Not necessarily. Not at all.]

948
00:47:27,030 --> 00:47:29,960
[Seungho: Right, you can't say it yet.]
[Jinwoo: No, no.]

949
00:47:30,760 --> 00:47:36,100
[Seungho wants someone older;
Jinwoo wants someone younger.
Will it work out for them?]

950
00:47:31,570 --> 00:47:33,570
I might be much older than you think.

951
00:47:33,920 --> 00:47:35,990
You'll see when it's revealed.

952
00:47:36,570 --> 00:47:39,380
-I'm a bit curious about your job. -Yeah.

953
00:47:36,900 --> 00:47:40,640
[Jinwoo: I'm a bit curious about your job.]

954
00:47:43,680 --> 00:47:44,590
My job.

955
00:47:47,580 --> 00:47:54,790
[Jinwoo: I have a guess.
Are you in art or sports?]

956
00:47:54,790 --> 00:47:57,460
[Seungho: I can't answer that.]
[Jinwoo: Right, you can't. I'm just guessing.]

957
00:47:57,460 --> 00:47:59,320
[Seungho: I could be unemployed.]

958
00:47:59,320 --> 00:48:03,060
[Jinwoo: Since you're young,
you might a freelancer.]

959
00:47:59,500 --> 00:48:00,560
Because I'm young.

960
00:48:03,060 --> 00:48:05,730
[Jinwoo: Or a college student.]

961
00:48:03,100 --> 00:48:05,630
-Or a college student. -That's possible too.

962
00:48:05,730 --> 00:48:10,270
[Seungho: Anyway, you already know I'm young.]
[Jinwoo: You're not even trying to hide it now.]

963
00:48:07,820 --> 00:48:08,950
Yes, I already know.

964
00:48:10,270 --> 00:48:15,610
[Seungho: I'm young, sure, but maybe
not as young as you think.]

965
00:48:16,980 --> 00:48:18,810
[Jinwoo: So not baby-level young?]

966
00:48:18,810 --> 00:48:22,010
[Seungho: I can't say that.]

967
00:48:19,750 --> 00:48:21,860
You can't say that. OK, OK, OK.

968
00:48:22,010 --> 00:48:26,550
[Seungho: Anyway, you all know I'm young.]

969
00:48:27,090 --> 00:48:29,660
[Seungho: Red wine ia a romantic drink, you know.]

970
00:48:29,660 --> 00:48:32,180
[Seungho: In that kind of mood,]

971
00:48:32,180 --> 00:48:34,050
[Seungho: chatting with someone I like]

972
00:48:34,050 --> 00:48:39,120
[Seungho: just makes me feel
more attracted to them.]

973
00:48:39,120 --> 00:48:41,790
[Seungho: Since it's still early,
everything feels so exciting.]

974
00:48:41,790 --> 00:48:45,260
[Seungho: And I feel very relaxed
at the same time. I love that.]

975
00:48:47,130 --> 00:48:50,600
[Jinwoo: Maybe it's because of the wine,
but I'm in a really good mood.]

976
00:48:50,600 --> 00:48:54,070
[Jinwoo: I think Seungho might
have feelings for me.]

977
00:48:54,070 --> 00:48:57,270
[Jinwoo: Maybe it's not just me feeling this way?]

978
00:48:57,270 --> 00:48:59,400
[Jinwoo: Just thinking about that
makes me so happy.]

979
00:48:59,400 --> 00:49:02,070
[Jinwoo: As long as we can keep this going,]

980
00:49:02,070 --> 00:49:03,940
[Jinwoo: I think we could finally be together.]

981
00:49:04,480 --> 00:49:09,010
[On the first night, they spent time together
in the secret room]

982
00:49:09,550 --> 00:49:14,090
[Jinwoo: Do you think the others are showering?]
[Seungho: I don't know. Wanna go check?]

983
00:49:17,020 --> 00:49:22,900
[Jinwoo: They're in the shower.]
[Seungho: I see. Let's just go get our stuff.]

984
00:49:20,590 --> 00:49:21,720
Let's go shower too.

985
00:49:25,820 --> 00:49:30,020
[What's going on?]

986
00:49:26,000 --> 00:49:27,250
-Hello. -What's going on?

987
00:49:27,250 --> 00:49:28,480
We...

988
00:49:30,020 --> 00:49:33,820
[Refusing to show the bare face]

989
00:49:30,840 --> 00:49:32,340
-Are you done showering? -Hello.

990
00:49:32,340 --> 00:49:33,160
Yes.

991
00:49:33,840 --> 00:49:37,310
[Seungho: So showing your bare face is a no-go?]
[Jinwoo: I've already seen it, though.]

992
00:49:37,310 --> 00:49:39,980
[Seungho: Can I see it too?]

993
00:49:38,410 --> 00:49:39,720
Out of nowhere...

994
00:49:39,970 --> 00:49:41,140
I wanna see it too.

995
00:49:39,980 --> 00:49:43,340
[Guarding it like a fortress]

996
00:49:41,680 --> 00:49:42,880
I didn't get to see it.

997
00:49:43,340 --> 00:49:46,650
[Hyeyeon: Why are you here?]
[Seungho: We came to get our stuff.]

998
00:49:46,650 --> 00:49:47,720
[Jinwoo: We came to get our shower stuff.]

999
00:49:47,720 --> 00:49:57,940
[Jinwoo: Bye, Hyeyeon. You must be tired.]
[Hyeyeon: Good night.]

1000
00:49:48,550 --> 00:49:50,280
-Bye, Hyeyeon. -Bye.

1001
00:49:53,070 --> 00:49:54,530
-Good night. -Good night.

1002
00:49:57,940 --> 00:50:02,540
[Yongkyu and Chaebe are already asleep]

1003
00:50:03,340 --> 00:50:06,410
[Yongkyu: Since it's the first day,
I'm a bit tired.]

1004
00:50:06,410 --> 00:50:09,500
[Yongkyu: I've been all over the place.]

1005
00:50:09,500 --> 00:50:13,660
[Yongkyu: Starting tomorrow, I'll do my best
and show everyone what I've got.]

1006
00:50:13,960 --> 00:50:20,420
[Chaebe: Heejin makes me feel very comfortable,
which is very nice.]

1007
00:50:20,420 --> 00:50:24,580
[Chaebe: Seungho left
a strong first impression on me.]

1008
00:50:25,140 --> 00:50:31,060
[Chaebe: And my ideal type, appearance-wise,
is Yongkyu. Those three.]

1009
00:50:31,060 --> 00:50:35,850
[Chaebe: Yeah, I'm interested in those three.]

1010
00:50:36,060 --> 00:50:40,260
[Eunchae: The two people I care about the most]

1011
00:50:40,260 --> 00:50:43,420
[Eunchae: are Kim Seungho and Go Sujin.]

1012
00:50:43,420 --> 00:50:45,720
[Eunchae: Since I made a big decision
to come to this show,]

1013
00:50:45,720 --> 00:50:50,530
[Eunchae: I'm gonna give it my best.]

1014
00:50:52,020 --> 00:50:56,180
[Sujin: I only showed
about 0.5% of my charm today.]

1015
00:50:56,180 --> 00:50:58,980
[Sujin: I was just laughing the whole time.]

1016
00:50:59,220 --> 00:51:01,260
[Sujin: Tomorrow, I'm going out with Heejin.]

1017
00:51:01,260 --> 00:51:06,500
[Sujin: I'm gonna find out her dating style,]

1018
00:51:06,500 --> 00:51:08,460
[Sujin: and see if we fit.]

1019
00:51:08,860 --> 00:51:12,900
[Hyeyeon: If I talk in my sleep,
promise you won't answer me.]

1020
00:51:12,900 --> 00:51:14,580
[Heejin: I promise.]

1021
00:51:14,580 --> 00:51:19,310
[Hyeyeon: Good night.]
[Heejin: Good night.]

1022
00:51:20,380 --> 00:51:24,380
[Hyeyeon: I might not have a chance
to date Seungho,]

1023
00:51:24,380 --> 00:51:26,250
[Hyeyeon: nor Sujin.]

1024
00:51:26,250 --> 00:51:29,990
[Hyeyeon: If only I had been more proactive]

1025
00:51:29,990 --> 00:51:33,720
[Hyeyeon: and taken the initiative
to talk to them.]

1026
00:51:34,260 --> 00:51:37,190
[Hyeyeon: But from now on,
I'll grab every chance I get.]

1027
00:51:37,990 --> 00:51:42,000
[Heejin: I gotta be more proactive, right?
Because it's only day one.]

1028
00:51:42,000 --> 00:51:45,730
[Heejin: I really need to put myself out there
and be more active.]

1029
00:51:46,800 --> 00:51:50,540
[Seungho: I feel like the time
we spent alone together]

1030
00:51:50,540 --> 00:51:55,340
[Seungho: helped me get to know Jinwoo
better and faster than anyone else.]

1031
00:51:55,340 --> 00:51:58,280
[Seungho: I don't want anyone else
using that room now.]

1032
00:51:58,280 --> 00:52:02,550
[Seungho: I wanna keep it for myself.]

1033
00:52:03,350 --> 00:52:05,750
[Jinwoo: I was quite worried on the first day.]

1034
00:52:05,750 --> 00:52:08,690
[Jinwoo: But it felt like I had
some kind of main character buff.]

1035
00:52:08,690 --> 00:52:10,560
[Jinwoo: Everything went really smoothly.]

1036
00:52:10,560 --> 00:52:14,830
[Jinwoo: I was lucky,
and I was really happy to meet Seungho.]

1037
00:52:14,830 --> 00:52:16,160
[Jinwoo: I even got picked.]

1038
00:52:16,700 --> 00:52:20,170
[Jinwoo: Everything I had hoped for
on the first day]

1039
00:52:20,170 --> 00:52:23,640
[Jinwoo: pretty much all happened,
so I was really happy.]

1040
00:52:24,440 --> 00:52:28,980
[The two in the secret room
are the last to fall asleep]

1041
00:52:28,980 --> 00:52:33,520
[Seungho: Why can't I breathe?
My nose is covered.]

1042
00:52:33,040 --> 00:52:34,710
-I'm fine. -You good?

1043
00:52:34,050 --> 00:52:40,720
[On the first night,
the two boys are joking around and laughing]

1044
00:52:35,430 --> 00:52:37,290
-I was just saying that. -Really?

1045
00:52:38,070 --> 00:52:40,130
I suddenly couldn't catch my breath.

1046
00:52:41,520 --> 00:52:46,060
[For some, it is a day of fulfillment.
For others, it is a day of regret.]

1047
00:52:46,600 --> 00:52:51,930
[What kind of encounters
are waiting for us tomorrow?]

1048
00:53:15,580 --> 00:53:17,540
[Stirs]

1049
00:53:21,660 --> 00:53:25,420
[Half awake]

1050
00:53:26,100 --> 00:53:30,370
[Sujin: I slept really deeply
because I was exhausted from the day before.]

1051
00:53:35,440 --> 00:53:39,710
[Sujin: The lighting was so good,
and the room was so bright. That was how I felt.]

1052
00:53:39,710 --> 00:53:42,120
[Sujin: I just kept thinking,]

1053
00:53:42,120 --> 00:53:46,780
[Sujin: "I can't believe
this is actually happening."]

1054
00:53:49,220 --> 00:53:52,860
[Moves]

1055
00:53:52,860 --> 00:53:56,140
[Jolts awake]

1056
00:54:01,100 --> 00:54:03,740
[Heejin: Ah, so hot.]

1057
00:54:18,980 --> 00:54:21,780
[Heejin: I slept really well,
even though I only slept a few hours.]

1058
00:54:21,780 --> 00:54:24,100
[Heejin: I wasn't tired at all the next morning.]

1059
00:54:24,100 --> 00:54:25,890
[Heejin: I woke up feeling refreshed.]

1060
00:54:26,860 --> 00:54:30,860
[Heejin's busy day begins]

1061
00:54:48,780 --> 00:54:50,940
[Peeks out]

1062
00:54:59,660 --> 00:55:01,980
[Heejin: Do you wanna get up?]
[Hyeyeon: OK.]

1063
00:55:01,980 --> 00:55:05,720
[Heejin: Did you sleep well? It's 8:35.]

1064
00:55:05,720 --> 00:55:09,190
[Hyeyeon: Really? Why didn't you wake me up?]

1065
00:55:09,190 --> 00:55:11,860
[Heejin: I wanted to let you sleep longer.
You looked so peaceful.]

1066
00:55:13,460 --> 00:55:16,390
[Heejin: Take your time getting ready.]

1067
00:55:19,060 --> 00:55:22,000
[Hyeyeon: I'm up.]

1068
00:55:22,000 --> 00:55:25,470
[Hyeyeon: I didn't sleep very well.
I was nervous, so I only slept for a bit.]

1069
00:55:25,470 --> 00:55:28,670
[Hyeyeon: Sleeping with strangers
in the same room makes me nervous.]

1070
00:55:28,670 --> 00:55:32,680
[Hyeyeon: And since it was the first day,
I was still really tense.]

1071
00:55:32,680 --> 00:55:37,480
[Hyeyeon: Has everyone else woken up?]

1072
00:55:37,480 --> 00:55:39,880
[Hyeyeon: It's so quiet.]

1073
00:55:39,880 --> 00:55:43,620
[Heejin: The ones in the triple room might be up.]
[Hyeyeon: Really? Ah, right.]

1074
00:55:43,620 --> 00:55:46,560
[Heejin: They're quite early risers.]

1075
00:55:46,560 --> 00:55:48,960
[Hyeyeon: Yeah.]

1076
00:55:52,160 --> 00:55:56,430
[Chaebe is the first of the three to wake up]

1077
00:55:56,700 --> 00:55:57,770
[Chaebe: I slept very well.]

1078
00:55:57,770 --> 00:56:00,710
[Chaebe: I fell asleep as soon as I lay down
and woke up the moment I opened my eyes.]

1079
00:56:00,970 --> 00:56:02,840
[Chaebe: "When do we meet?"]

1080
00:56:02,840 --> 00:56:04,180
[Chaebe: "When are we gathering?"]

1081
00:56:04,180 --> 00:56:06,040
[Chaebe: "When should I start getting ready?"]

1082
00:56:06,040 --> 00:56:08,450
[Chaebe: I think those were the only things
on my mind.]

1083
00:56:20,190 --> 00:56:23,660
[Eunchae: Maybe it was because
it was the first night,]

1084
00:56:23,660 --> 00:56:26,330
[Eunchae: but I was a bit nervous
and didn't sleep well.]

1085
00:56:31,980 --> 00:56:36,220
[Covering the face]

1086
00:56:41,010 --> 00:56:42,880
[Eunchae: Did you sleep well?]

1087
00:56:42,880 --> 00:56:45,020
[Chaebe: I slept very well.]

1088
00:56:45,020 --> 00:56:46,890
[Chaebe: Incredibly well.]

1089
00:56:47,940 --> 00:56:49,100
[Peeks]

1090
00:56:49,100 --> 00:56:52,220
[The first morning together,
with a roommate who's still a bit awkward]

1091
00:56:52,660 --> 00:56:56,140
[Chaebe: Eunchae and I weren't that familiar yet.]

1092
00:56:56,140 --> 00:56:57,470
[Chaebe: We weren't very close.]

1093
00:56:57,470 --> 00:57:02,380
[Chaebe: But Yongkyu and I shared a bed.]

1094
00:57:02,380 --> 00:57:03,380
[Chaebe: Since we're both guys,]

1095
00:57:03,380 --> 00:57:07,820
[Chaebe: I felt a bit more comfortable around him.
I mean, just a tiny bit.]

1096
00:57:08,700 --> 00:57:10,820
[Ah...]

1097
00:57:11,420 --> 00:57:13,900
[Peeps out]

1098
00:57:14,380 --> 00:57:16,380
[Yongkyu: Why am I so tired? Ugh!]

1099
00:57:16,380 --> 00:57:17,100
[Haha]

1100
00:57:17,100 --> 00:57:20,780
[Haha]
[Yongkyu: I'm tired no matter how much I sleep.]

1101
00:57:21,500 --> 00:57:23,780
[Ugh...]

1102
00:57:23,820 --> 00:57:25,770
[Yongkyu: Tired? Want more sleep?]

1103
00:57:25,770 --> 00:57:28,170
[Yongkyu: Some people might need an hour,]

1104
00:57:28,170 --> 00:57:29,500
[Yongkyu: or even two, to get ready.]

1105
00:57:29,500 --> 00:57:35,910
[Yongkyu: But for me, it only takes
about 10 to 15 minutes.]

1106
00:57:35,910 --> 00:57:38,050
[Yongkyu: So I planned to wake up a bit later.]

1107
00:57:38,050 --> 00:57:40,720
[Yongkyu: That way, they could get ready first.]

1108
00:57:43,020 --> 00:57:47,920
[Waking up late is Yongkyu's way
of being considerate to his roommates]

1109
00:57:48,220 --> 00:57:51,660
[In the sweet secret room...]

1110
00:57:53,100 --> 00:57:55,740
[Turns head]

1111
00:57:55,780 --> 00:57:59,130
[Jinwoo: How was your sleep?]
[Seungho: Not sure, honestly.]

1112
00:57:59,130 --> 00:57:59,930
[Jinwoo: Really?]

1113
00:57:59,930 --> 00:58:02,870
[Seungho: I feel like I slept, but I'm not sure.]

1114
00:58:02,870 --> 00:58:05,270
[Jinwoo: I only slept for a little while.
I was awake most of the night.]

1115
